_number":601,"text_uthmani":"فَجَعَلَهُمۡ كَعَصۡفٖ مَّأۡكُولِۭ ٥","text_indopak":"فَجَعَلَهُمۡ كَعَصۡفٍ مَّاۡكُوۡلٍ‏","text_uthmani_tajweed":"فَجَعَلَهُمْ كَعَصْ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>فٍ م</tajweed>َّأْك<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed>لِۭ <span class=end>٥</span>"}],"source":"cache","cachedAt":"2026-07-04T02:22:15.999Z"}